author: martinc
msg: Checkstyle rules for Struts. This file is almost the same as Maven's sun_checks.xml with minimal changes for:
- RegExp based file header check, since we use $Id$ in the file headers.
- Struts has always used "this.foo = foo", so make that not an error.
- Disable two specific error types that would cause backward compatibility changes if we fixed them (and they seem odd to me anyway).
Full details of the differences are in a comment within this file.
